@startuml
title Activity Diagram 3: Kitchen Processing Flow

skinparam activityFontSize 12
skinparam activityArrowFontSize 10

start

note right
  Prerequisites:
  Payment successful
  Order status PAID
  Notification sent
end note

:Receive Order Notification;
:Display on Kitchen Screen;
:Play Sound Alert;
:View Order Details;

note right
  Order includes:
  Table number / Items
  Special notes / Order time
end note

:Add to Cooking Queue;
:Start Preparing Food;
:Update Status IN KITCHEN;
:Cook Food Items;

note right
  Estimated Times:
  Indomie 5-7 min
  Roti Bakar 3-5 min  
  Nasi 7-10 min
end note

:Quality Check;
:Mark as Complete;
:Update Status READY;

fork
  :Notify Customer;
fork again
  :Update Kitchen Display;
end fork

:Customer Receives Alert;
:Customer Goes to Pickup Counter;
:Hand Over Order;
:Update Status SERVED;
:Customer Consumes Food;
:Customer Leaves Table;
:Update Status COMPLETED;
:Save to Order History;
:Update Sales Statistics;

note right
  Complete Lifecycle:
  Order placed -> Payment processed
  Kitchen prepared -> Customer served
  Order completed
end note

stop

@enduml
